    - NodeJS is a server side Scripting Language.
    - By using NodeJS We Can Create our own servers with port number.
    - NodeJS Application itself acting as a Business Components as well as server.

Modules in NodeJS.

1.express
    - used to develop the Restful Services in Node Application.

2.body-parser
    - used to set the MIME Type.
    Ex.

        JSON
        XML
        CSV
        Text
        --
        --
        --

3.mysql
    - used to interact with the MySQL DataBase.

4.mongodb
    - used to interact with the mongodb.

5.fs
    - used to interact with the flat files.

6.jwt-simple

    - used to maintain the Token Based Authentication System.


